entries.detail:
PostgreSQL Tables:
users (id, username, email, password_hash)
videos (id, user_id, title, raw_video_url, processed_hls_url, status)
comments (id, video_id, user_id, content)
subscriptions (subscriber_id, channel_id)

Redis Keys:
rate_limit:ip:{ip}
video_meta:{id}
upload_session:{user}:{session}

Request: POST /api/v1/videos/upload-url
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
Payload: { fileName: string, fileSize: number, contentType: string }
Response 200: { uploadUrl: string, videoId: string, expiresAt: string }

Request: POST /api/v1/videos/{videoId}/publish
Headers: Authorization: Bearer <jwt>
Payload: { title: string, description: string }
Response 201: { id: string, status: 'processing' }
